Swann</b> is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\">House Swann</a>. In the appendix of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> he is listed as the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> despite the fact that the earlier established Lord of Stonehelm, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gulian_Swann\" title=\"Gulian Swann\">Gulian Swann</a>, had two sons, <a href=\"/index.php/Donnel_Swann\" title=\"Donnel Swann\">Donnel</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Swann\" title=\"Balon Swann\">Balon</a>, the former of which is still eligible to inherit.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clifford_Swann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403183511\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.114 seconds\nReal time u